s":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-d4","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":279,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/12\/19\/allah-punish-stealing-land\/","url_meta":{"origin":810,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Theft: Allah will punish the usurper of land","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa'id ibn Zayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever wrongly seizes a plot of land, Allah will make him carry seven earths around his neck.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1610 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":763,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/08\/do-you-know-the-bankrupt\/","url_meta":{"origin":810,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Iqtisas: Do you know who the truly bankrupt are?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\u201cDo you know who are bankrupt?\u201d They said, \u201cThe one without money or goods is bankrupt.\u201d The Prophet said,\u00a0\u201cVerily, the bankrupt of my nation are those who come on the Day of Resurrection with prayers, fasting, and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19921,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/10\/08\/umar-ask-sheep-euphrates\/","url_meta":{"origin":810,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Rights: I fear Allah will ask me about my animals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 8, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Dawud ibn Ali reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf a lost sheep under my care were to die on the banks of the Euphrates, I would expect Allah the Exalted to question me about it on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 137\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25566,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/06\/darkness-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":810,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Oppression: Injustice will be darkness on Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 6, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, oppression will be darkness on the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2447, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2579 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064